   <joint name="alt_camera_joint1" type="fixed">
      <origin rpy="1.5916 0 0" xyz="1.066 -0.07 0.04"/>

and:
   <horizontal_fov>1.65</horizontal_fov>

Conversion from pixel (i,j) --> (x,y,z)/system_ref_frame
on ground plane, z=0

K_pix = 160 pixels/meter
i0 = 506
j0 = -78

x/sys = (j-j0)/K_pix
y/sys = (i-i0)/K_pix 
